==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Medic
<hw>Med"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who serves to
provide medical care.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>A
member of the medical corps in the military.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A medical doctor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>A medical student.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

